{"type": "article", "id": 18666, "title": "带多孔结构的户外椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-08T07:42:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141013kq2OxKfyYTmXFp4n.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一张可以放在户外的椅子，靠背和座位上面的多孔结构能让雨水自然流走。而铝制框架连接了高分子聚丙烯打造的座位和靠背，可以多张椅子叠加起来，因而有更强的环境适应力。它可以放在餐饮等商业场所，也能放在家中当备用的椅子，有黑、白、米、珊瑚红以及黑灰色 5 种颜色。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141012p3UN8ZPDrLQuBtVw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141012Wg2P3sKTJnZcaHX9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141013NWkH1ZfYTJ5tmCRD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66452991\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}